<br>
I don't think Yale did anything terrible, he didn't edit the posts and change the content just moved it to the Nuclear Waste forum... I don't have the time or the patience to moderate... and whoever the mod is here, needs some leeway, otherwise I end up indirectly being the moderator...<br>
